author: eva.vance
content: Hi all) My name is Eva. My team and I are currently developing an AI. If you could help us determine the effectiveness, that would be cool. From you a short interview before you start using it, usage within a month, and a final interview and evaluation of cost-effectiveness and efficiency.Write to me, I will tell you what it can do and what functions it performs.
